{"tid":1676141,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【嚴正聲明五大訴求缺一不可】估計政府會放風降民憤 設立獨立調查委員會 瓦解運動","createTime":"2019-10-26T09:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T12:44:41.000Z","uid":278392,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d1f2d32789d39ac5410c5f2743a789a71f6a967b","tid":1676141,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:12:32.000Z","msg":"南早引消息：若公眾不滿監警會報告　政府考慮設獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676044</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n政府態度軟化 就好似之前撤回送中咁 應承一個訴求等部分人收貨降低民憤<br />\n先唔講獨立調查有冇用 五大訴求差一個都唔可以接受<br />\n仲有解散警隊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />獨立調查佢地驚閪咩 根本成個警隊制度都有問題<br />\n嚴正聲明 香港人係未實現五大訴求之前絕不讓步<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可呀屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n黑警我屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"4add5f66713a20787705162cde11010c0001c31e","tid":1676141,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:13:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警</strong>得罪中央犯死罪</span>，已<span style=\"color: red;\">大禍臨頭</span>！<br />\n+ <span style=\"color: gold;\">送條妙計<strong>俾科士解圍</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671833\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671833</a>"},{"pid":"72807c35d6a3babc9036919ee6c2bb618f024d45","tid":1676141,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:13:34.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好屌我p牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4dfe1915414cd43176a12b88f012134ca7a1427","tid":1676141,"uid":278392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"